```

### 8. Generated Prompt Enhancement

When `confidenceScore >= 60%`:

```xml
<repo_background>
  <stack>
    <tech>TypeScript</tech>
    <tech>Next.js</tech>
  </stack>
  <detected_context confidence="85%">
    <runtime>node</runtime>
    <architecture>Next.js App Router</architecture>
    <package_manager>npm</package_manager>
    <testing_framework>Vitest</testing_framework>
    <detection_sources>package.json, file structure</detection_sources>
  </detected_context>
  ...
</repo_background>
```

### 9. ADR Context Update

**Detected stack (conf >= 60%):**
```
Context: "Analyse automatique du repository cible (confiance: 85%).
          Stack détectée: TypeScript, Next.js."
```

**Default stack:**
```
Context: "Pour développer [name] (saas), nous devons choisir
          une stack technique moderne et adaptée."
```

