## Benefits

1. **Programmatic Integration** - Structured data can be used in code logic
2. **Confidence Thresholding** - Only trust high-quality detections
3. **Enhanced Recommendations** - Skills matched to actual project stack
4. **Better Prompts** - LLM receives accurate project context
5. **Maintainability** - Clear separation: data → presentation

## Migration Path

No migration needed - changes are additive and backward compatible.

Existing workflows continue to function identically.

